te-accordion/items.description: Array with the title for accordion component. Slots correspond to `content-{key}` with key beginning on zero

te-accordion/flush.description: Indicates when to show the border line. By default false

te-alert/text.description: Main message for alert. It will be replaced by slot default

te-alert/solid.description: Indicates when to use a solid background color. By default is false

te-badge/text.description: Text to show into the badge

te-badge/solid.description: Indicates when to use a solid background color. By default is false

te-badge/rounded.description: Indicates when is full rounded. By default is false

te-badge/outlined.description: Indicates when badge only has a colored border. By default is false

te-button/buttonType.description: Native button behaviour. By default, button

te-button/rounded.description: Indicates when is full rounded. By default is false

te-button/outlined.description: Indicates when button only has a colored border. By default is false

te-button/shadowed.description: Indicates when button has a small shadow around it. By default is false

te-button/uppercased.description: Indicates when button text is all UPPERCASED. By default is false

te-button/onlyText.description: Indicates when button will only show the text without any other element. By default is false

te-button/noRounded.description: Indicates when button has a small rounded corner. By default is false

te-button/disabled.description: Indicates when button is disabled. By default is false

te-button/loading.description: Indicates the loading state for button. By default is false

te-button/ripple.description: Indicates when to show the ripple effect on the button. By default is false

te-button/icon.description: Indicates when button is to show only an icon. By default is false

te-button-group/quantity.description: The number of buttons to show. By default 1

te-button-group/outlined.description: Indicates when buttons only will have a colored border. By default is false

te-button-group/disabled.description: This array corresponds to disability to each button according with its index

te-card/imgSrc.description: Source to show into the main card image.

te-card/width.description: Indicates the card width. By default 350px

te-card/hasHeader.description: Indicate when card has header. By default false

te-card/hasFooter.description: Indicate when card has footer. By default false

te-card/shadowless.description: Indicate when card will have a shadow around it. By default is false.

te-checkbox/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-checkbox/disabled.description: Indicates when checkbox is disabled. By default is false

te-switch/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-switch/disabled.description: Indicates when switch is disabled. By default is false

te-radio/idInput.description: String to indicate the id for radio input. By default is an UUID

te-radio/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-radio/nativeValue.description: Value to set into radio input.

te-select/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-select/options.description: Options to show into the select input

te-select/displayField.description: Field name to show in select options. By default is `label`

te-select/valueField.description: Field name to use with v-model directive. By default is `id`

te-select/size.description: Select input size. By default is `medium`

te-select/disabled.description: Indicates when input is disabled. By default is false

te-breadcrumb/options.description: Array of object with options to show on breadcrumb

te-breadcrumb/separator.description: Character used as separator. By default is `/`

te-breadcrumb/linkTag.description: Name of the link tag. By default is `a`

te-textarea/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-textarea/disabled.description: Indicates when textarea is disabled. By default is false

te-textarea/rows.description: Number to set the textarea rows. By default is 3

te-textarea/cols.description: Number to set the textarea columns. By default is null

te-input/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-input/id.description: String to indicate the id for radio input. By default is an UUID

te-input/type.description: Value to set the input type. By default is text

te-input/disabled.description: Indicates when input is disabled. By default is false

te-input/form.description: Form name if it belongs to one

te-input/maxlength.description: Max length value for the input

te-input/minlength.description: Max length value for the input

te-input/pattern.description: Regular expression to apply on the input

te-input/readonly.description: Indicates when input is readonly. By default is false

te-input/step.description: Indicates the step for numeric inputs.

te-input/invalid.description: Indicates when input is invalid. By default is false

te-input/helperText.description: Text to use as helper or hint text. Shown below the input

te-input/floating.description: Indicates when placeholder is floating. Size is not applied when floating is used.

te-input/rightIcon.description: Indicates the name of the icon used on the right side

te-input/rightIconClickable.description: Indicate if right icon is clickable emitting `right-icon-click` event. By default is false.

te-input/leftIcon.description: Indicates the name of the icon used on the left side.

te-input/leftIconClickable.description: Indicate if right icon is clickable emitting `left-icon-click` event. By default is false.

te-date-picker/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-date-picker/monthNames.description: Array with the name of the months. By default is the name of months in English

te-date-picker/days.description: Array with the name of the days. By default is the name of days in English

te-date-picker/disabled.description: Indicates when input is disabled. By default is false

te-date-picker/maxDate.description: Indicate the max selectable date on the input

te-date-picker/minDate.description: Indicate the min selectable date on the input

te-date-picker/notAllowedDates.description: Array to disable some dates from input.

te-time-picker/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive. This is a timestamp value

te-time-picker/ampm.description: Indicates when to show the option for AM/PM. By default is true

te-time-picker/disabled.description: Indicates when input is disabled. By default is false

te-range/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-range/min.description: Min value for the input. By default is 0

te-range/max.description: Max value for the input. By default is 5

te-range/step.description: The amount to advance from one value to another. By default is 1.

te-range/disabled.description: Indicates when input is disabled. By default is false

te-progress/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-progress/size.description: Value to indicate the progress size. By default is medium

te-progress/showValue.description: Value to indicate when to show the current step value. By default is false.

te-tabs/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive. This values indicates the current selected tab beginning on 0

te-tabs/titles.description: An array with the titles for the tabs

te-tabs/filled.description: Boolean value to indicate when tabs are solid colored

te-tabs/vertical.description: Boolean value to indicate when tabs are vertical

te-tabs/pills.description: Boolean value to indicate when show pills instead of tabs

te-list-group/items.description: An array with items to show into the list. You have slots like this: `item-{key}` with key beginning at 0 or the name field

te-list-group/clickable.description: Boolean value to indicate when list is clickable

te-list-group/activeItem.description: Value to indicate the active item

te-list-group/flush.description: Indicates when to show the border line. By default false

te-dropdown/size.description: Value to indicate the dropdown size. By default is medium

te-dropdown/outlined.description: Value to indicate when dropdown trigger only has a border

te-dropdown/label.description: Text to show as dropdown label

te-dropdown/ripple.description: Indicates when to show the ripple effect on the dropdown trigger. By default is false

te-dropdown-item/disabled.description: Indicates when dropdown is disabled. By default is false

te-modal/title.description: Text to show as modal  title

te-modal/visible.description: Boolean value to show modal. By default is false.

te-modal/showCloseButton.description: Boolean value to show the close button. By default is true.

te-modal/hideHeader.description: Boolean value to show the modal header. By default is true.

te-modal/hideFooter.description: Boolean value to show the modal footer. By default is true.

te-modal/scrollable.description: Boolean value to indicate when modal is scrollable. By default is false.

te-modal/centered.description: Boolean value to indicate when modal is centered on screen. By default is false.

te-modal/size.description: Value to indicate the modal size

te-spinner/size.description: Value to indicate the spinner size. By default medium

te-spinner/color.description: Value to indicate the color size

te-stepper/steps.description: Array containing the title used on the component

te-stepper/activeStep.description: Indicate what step is current active. You can use .sync modifier

te-stepper/color.description: Indicate the stepper color. By default is primary

te-toast/title.description: Text to use as toast title

te-toast/subtitle.description: Text to use as toast subtitle

te-toast/message.description: Text to use as secondary text

te-toast/showCloseButton.description: Value to indicate when to show the close button. By default is true.

te-toast/color.description: Value to set the toast background color

te-pagination/pages.description: The number of pages to show on pagination component. By default is 3

te-pagination/activePage.description: The positive number of the actived page. You can use .sync modifier. By default is 1

te-pagination/pagesToShow.description: Number of pages to show on the pagination component. By default is 3.

te-pagination/showIcons.description: Value to show the icon on next and prev buttons. By default is false.

te-pagination/rounded.description: Value to set the pagination buttons rounded. By default is false.

te-pagination/size.description: Value to set the pagination buttons size. By default is medium

te-pagination/position.description: Value to set pagination alignment. By default is center

te-pagination/labelNext.description: Text to show on next button. By default is `Next`

te-pagination/labelPrev.description: Text to show on prev button. By default is `Prev`

te-navbar/hrefHeader.description: String to indicate the path when clicking on navbar logo. This is used for a and router-link tags. By default is `#`

te-navbar/dark.description: Boolean value to indicate when nav header is dark. By default is false.

te-navbar/headerTag.description: Tag used for header link tag. By default is a.

te-navbar-item/href.description: String used as path. This is used for a and router-link tags. By default is `#`

te-navbar-item/dark.description: Boolean value to indicate when nav header item is dark. By default is false.

te-navbar-item/disabled.description: Boolean value to indicate when input is disabled. By default is false

te-navbar-item/tag.description: Tag used for header link tag. By default is a.

te-table/items.description: Array of object to  show into the table

te-table/headers.description: Array of object with the columns to show into the table

te-table/striped.description: Boolean value to indicate when table is striped. By default is false.

te-table/hoverable.description: Boolean value to indicate when table has a row hover effect. By default is false.

te-table/bordered.description: Boolean value to indicate when table has border around it. By default is false.

te-table/centered.description: Boolean value to indicate when table headers are centered. By default is false.

te-table/borderless.description: Boolean value to indicate when table does not have borders. By default is false.

te-table/compact.description: Boolean value to indicate when table has smaller rows. By default is false.

te-table/responsive.description: Boolean value to indicate when table will show a scroll on small devices. By default is true.

te-table/headerType.description: String to indicate the header background color. By default is `normal`

te-table/search.description: String to search on shown items on the table

te-table/noDataLabel.description: Text to show when there is no coincidence when searching. You can override this value using no-data slots. By default is `No data`

te-table/hasSubheading.description: Indicate when table has a subheader before the items. By default false.

te-table/showRowNum.description: Boolean value to indicate when table will show the row numbers. By default is false.

te-table/rowNumLabel.description: String to show on the row numbers column when prop is true. By default is `#`

te-table/itemPerPage.description: Number of pages to show on the pagination component. By default is 3.

te-table/paginationAlign.description: Value to set pagination alignment. By default is center

te-table/labelNext.description: Text to show on next button. By default is `Next`

te-table/labelPrev.description: Text to show on prev button. By default is `Prev`

te-table/loading.description: Boolean value to indicate when data on table is being loaded. By default is false

te-file/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive (base64 string passed or array of base64 string)

te-file/accept.description: String with the files' extensions on the input

te-file/disabled.description: Indicates when input is disabled. By default is false

te-file/multiple.description: Indicates when input accept select multiple files.

te-file/size.description: Value to set input size. By default medium

te-notification/text.description: Text used as notification main text

te-notification/position.description: String to set the notification position. By default is top-right

te-notification/color.description: String to indicate the notification color. By default is primary

te-notification/hide.description: Value to indicate when to hide the notification. By default is false.

te-icon/name.description: Name of the icon to use on the component. Only compatible with Glyphicons or Bootstrap Icons.

te-rating/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive

te-rating/quantity.description: Number of icons to show into rating input.

te-rating/icon.description: The name to use as icon. By default is `star-fill`

te-rating/iconSizeClass.description: String to set class(es) for the icon span.

te-rating/spacing.description: Value to set the spacing between icons. By defaul is 1

te-rating/disabled.description: Indicates when rating is disabled. By default is false

te-rating/color.description: String value to use as icon color. You can use a string, hex or rgb(a) value. By default is yellow

te-rating/hasHalfValues.description: Boolean value to indicate when input has half scores. By default is false.

te-rating/clearable.description: Boolean value to indicate when input is clearable. By default is false

te-toast-light/title.description: Text to use as toast title

te-toast-light/subtitle.description: Text to use as toast subtitle

te-toast-light/type.description: Tost type. By default is info.

te-offcanvas/value.description: Prop to use with v-model directive. This prop indicates when to show or hide the drawer

te-offcanvas/title.description: String to show as drawer title
